    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 It is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s as close to perfect as it gets. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
